# Wallet — Tirelire et transactions
# Toutes les routes nécessitent un JWT (obtenir via auth/verify-otp)

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Mon wallet (créé si absent)
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Enregistrer un versement Tirelire (saving)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transaction
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 5000,
  "type": "saving",
  "gateway_ref": "feda_xxx"
}

### Autres types : rent, commission, withdrawal
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transaction
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": 25000,
  "type": "rent"
}

### Liste de mes transactions
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
